The paper deals with algebraic branching programs (ABPs) and their computational limitations, which are topics in computational complexity (cs.CC) and data structures (cs.DS). The paper also involves the study of polynomials and their properties, which falls under the category of symbolic computation (cs.SC) and discrete mathematics (cs.DM).
